Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.50,0:00:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于由敌联盟发起的对我校袭击的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.14,0:00:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雄英高中英雄科一年A班20名学生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.47,0:00:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前往承办各种灾害救援训练的假想灾害事故场简称USJ的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.61,0:00:24.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在课程开始之前受到了自称是敌联盟团体的袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.95,0:00:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌联盟组织的个性把学生们分散到了各个救援训练场
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.36,0:00:36.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,负责课程的教师相泽消太和13号在和敌的对抗中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.90,0:00:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,13号被自称黑雾的敌打伤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.00,0:00:47.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相泽也因受到了主犯死柄木另以及名为脑无的敌的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.41,0:00:49.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时无法战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.81,0:00:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迟来的教师欧尔麦特也参加了战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.85,0:00:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然负伤 但是击退了脑无扭转了局势
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.66,0:01:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且A班班长饭田天哉找到了在校的职业英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.86,0:01:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因职业英雄的救援 所以事件立刻结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.60,0:01:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果就是教师三名 学生一名负伤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.24,0:01:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此学校必须负起管理责任
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.51,0:01:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是学校决定在事件结束后立刻恢复英雄科的正常学习生活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.75,0:01:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让学生们掌握如何在混乱中拯救群众对扰敌人的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.86,0:01:41.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高中三年的时间实在太短了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.86,0:01:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还请家长们认同这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然给一年A班的学生家长们添了很大的麻烦以及让各位担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.61,0:01:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还是希望你们能多加理解多加协助
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.94,0:02:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雄英高中英雄科一年A班班主任相泽消太
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.82,0:02:06.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自敌联盟袭击4天后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.92,0:02:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一年级A班又到了雄英高中训练场USJ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.43,0:02:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然发生了这样的事情 可是上课就是上课
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.87,0:02:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以让我们认真的开始救援训练吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,13号老师你已经可以活动了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.71,0:02:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是背后被撕烂了一点 和前辈比起来这不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓 只要能上课就行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.48,0:02:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之赶快开始时间都被浪费了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.62,0:02:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相泽老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.95,0:02:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.15,0:02:44.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前还看到13号老师和相泽老师以及欧尔麦特老师来着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.33,0:02:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欧尔麦特老师怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.63,0:02:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 那种人不用管他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.20,0:02:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:55.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道欧尔麦特和相泽老师有矛盾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.89,0:03:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭大黑_GBK\b0\i1\\fs56\c&H04C8F9&\pos(515.195,520)}拯救吧！救援训练！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.71,0:03:04.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 首先是山区救援训练
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:10.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,训练的内容是三名登山者不小心跌落山谷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中一名脑部受到剧烈撞击昏迷不醒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其余两名腿部骨折无法活动正在呼救
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:26.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好深 那两个人竟然只摔断了腿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:29.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切岛君上鸣君你们在乐什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是刻不容缓的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.07,0:03:36.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吗 放心吧我一定会救你出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.71,0:03:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也太兴奋了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面没人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.85,0:03:42.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 就像真的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起加油吧 小久
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.65,0:03:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是靠的好近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从欧尔麦特那儿得到的力量 是拯救别人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.79,0:03:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须要尽快熟练掌握
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.36,0:04:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么伤者是我随机选的这三个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.77,0:04:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是竟然是被救援的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.81,0:04:08.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两位 我们要尽全力的变成伤者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.91,0:04:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装成伤者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.55,0:04:12.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.61,0:04:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 救援者就是你们4个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.58,0:04:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以使用那边的救援工具
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.85,0:04:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我必须救废久
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是剧情需要哦 小爆豪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.76,0:04:28.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅雨你别说这种会刺激爆豪的话了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁来救救我啊 腿断了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.23,0:04:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要开始了 谁先下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别太嚣张了 半身混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不用下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.54,0:04:44.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把山谷炸掉就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.78,0:04:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你疯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.28,0:04:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆豪也算是想了办法 只不过这不是正常人想的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:53.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一和绿谷扒上关系那家伙就变得好危险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.39,0:05:00.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八百万 你制造出滑轮做成滑轮组
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把昏迷不醒的伤者一个个的运上来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:05.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,常暗作为照顾伤者的人员下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后由我、爆豪、八百万拉上来…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许擅自决定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.11,0:05:12.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 爆豪同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.01,0:05:14.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最佳方素
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是抱着玩玩的心走的话 可以什么都不用做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没时间浪费在这种训练的争执上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁抱着玩玩的心态了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.26,0:05:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.26,0:05:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个真去脸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我们还有马上要做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们放心吧 我们马上来救你们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.67,0:05:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们趁算来了 得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.71,0:05:52.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁之先和伤者接触 这是第一要务
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.05,0:05:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多人在绝望的环境下会陷入恐慌状态
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:06:01.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先安抚这些人才能展开迅速的救援
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.06,0:06:03.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种训练？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.33,0:06:06.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不认真去做 你训的哪门子的练
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 八百万很优秀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.34,0:06:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真优（挺）秀（拔）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.22,0:06:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,常暗同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.76,0:06:27.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会用另外一根绳索把担架放下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.79,0:06:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你慢慢来就行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 常暗同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽日同学 已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了 我们大家都得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:41.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.14,0:06:44.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先把昏迷不醒的丽日同学运上去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解 啊 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的腿受伤了 不能帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:52.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不觉得让头部受伤的人一个人待着很危险吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.66,0:07:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都是两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有这个面积的阴影应该没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.83,0:07:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑影把丽日同学抱上去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好哆嗦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.44,0:07:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:13.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搬就好了吧搬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.97,0:07:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要撑着担架上升 别撞着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.71,0:07:18.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.85,0:07:22.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑影真是好厉害的个性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑影的真正价值可不是干这种杂活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.45,0:07:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它有着广阔的活动空间和灵活的身手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.45,0:07:30.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 我就知道它很有价值
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.46,0:07:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在什么地方都能派上用场 超帅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.80,0:07:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个奇怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.20,0:07:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已确保安全
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.24,0:07:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们 英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽日同学你在笑什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.64,0:07:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为饭田同学那个认真的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.25,0:07:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能憋住没笑真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.22,0:07:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饭田同学的表现很棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.25,0:08:00.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是可笑的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 虽然知道 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.19,0:08:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么接着放下一个了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴 别指挥我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.10,0:08:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵活运用个性来拯救别人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.23,0:08:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为救援小组来说真是高效率的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.44,0:08:20.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是超人社会应有的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.37,0:08:23.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是有一个人在拖后腿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好哆嗦 闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在自己的个性派不上用场情况下 这种行为是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.15,0:08:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因材适用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.59,0:08:36.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近有很多职业英雄做不到这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.79,0:08:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是强调着我来我来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.69,0:08:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果反而导致情况恶化的例子也有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要好好理解这点掌握后援工作的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.60,0:08:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定会成为优秀的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.40,0:08:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 优不优秀不好说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等会儿宰了你 那个酱油脸混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.71,0:09:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 最后一组
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梅雨可能会有点可怕不过尽量不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.59,0:09:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要来了 绿谷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽日同学 可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.90,0:09:18.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解除
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.47,0:09:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已确保安全
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.53,0:09:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小绿谷快放下我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.60,0:09:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.91,0:09:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有我骨折了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.24,0:09:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个体位是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救援对象全部救援成功
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.75,0:09:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 结束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用绳子就能让伤者平躺着浮上来再接住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.82,0:09:44.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好～狡～猾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也算不上狡猾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.59,0:09:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从第一次救援来讲 大家都做的很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.87,0:09:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救援工作是和时间战斗的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.37,0:09:57.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家还有不少要改进的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.54,0:10:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说大家还有不少进步的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.17,0:10:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉进步不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:03.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别松懈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.21,0:10:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,课程还在继续
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.18,0:10:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是坍塌地区
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这是你们第一次进行救援工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.89,0:10:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这次让你们体验一下各种各样的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.49,0:10:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坍塌地区救援工作内容是不知道伤者的数量和位置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在震后的都市中尽量救援伤者的训练
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.87,0:10:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到限定时间8分钟为止 4人一组展开救援行动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:37.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的16名同学挑选自己喜欢的地方藏起来等待救援
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.31,0:10:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是其中8名同学不能发出求救声
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.88,0:10:44.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此8名同学由我来指定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.05,0:10:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这不就是捉迷藏吗 捉迷藏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简要的说和捉迷藏很相似
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.29,0:10:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么第一场的4人组 就是你们4个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:58.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我要和废久一起行动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.87,0:11:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法啊 这是剧情需要…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.08,0:11:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了 说这种话会冷场的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.77,0:11:07.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮助伤者的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.67,0:11:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是万不得已碰到胸部的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:12.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好有罪恶感
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.05,0:11:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经出局了 峰田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从被救援者藏好已过2分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么搜索训练开始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.49,0:11:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要记住在地震刚刚结束的情况下发生什么都不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.89,0:11:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 出发
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.49,0:11:30.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 先寻找血迹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.30,0:11:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别指挥我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.40,0:11:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我来 垃圾们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.90,0:11:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 真是个自我主义的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.27,0:11:44.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法 总之我们先分散到视线和声音能传达到的四角
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.44,0:11:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.58,0:11:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救援工作是和时间战斗的工作要迅速进行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,0K
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.45,0:11:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.09,0:12:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,焦冻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:19.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能倒在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是我的最高杰作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让你如愿的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.14,0:12:36.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那是什么表情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.84,0:12:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.35,0:12:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不是英雄该有的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.82,0:12:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是何方神圣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.39,0:12:54.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都4天了让我好好大闹一番吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.16,0:12:56.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4天前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,袭击的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.30,0:12:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌联盟的残党
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.43,0:13:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是藏起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.47,0:13:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.42,0:13:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.39,0:13:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现尾白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.22,0:13:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绿谷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.39,0:13:28.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.06,0:13:29.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上下来救你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:33.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.07,0:13:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要用俺的超粘性小球吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.87,0:13:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加上瓦片的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:39.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简易梯子完成l
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.37,0:13:41.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尾白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.04,0:13:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,避开球体爬上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.48,0:13:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.08,0:13:48.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亏你能想出这么厉害的点子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.08,0:13:52.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从以前开始就比较喜欢考虑怎么去活用英雄们的个性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.65,0:13:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现小响香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.66,0:14:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为绝对不会被找到的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:02.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽日！耳郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.89,0:14:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.76,0:14:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不是应该是被救援的那方吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.43,0:14:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.17,0:14:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是敌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.51,0:14:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会出现在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.34,0:14:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是之前藏起来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.05,0:14:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会 难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.32,0:14:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,班上最强的都被…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.45,0:14:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说 赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.62,0:14:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们赶紧去老师那边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.42,0:14:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.79,0:14:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.53,0:14:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.36,0:14:36.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.66,0:14:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 有敌的残党
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.37,0:14:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在有伤在身
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.97,0:14:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在身体并不能战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.94,0:14:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.64,0:14:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 那么 你们就快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.18,0:14:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着正面的出口 快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.18,0:14:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不会让你们逃出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.18,0:15:00.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都统统给我去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.27,0:15:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.73,0:15:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是有多强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.37,0:15:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种家伙一直都藏在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.97,0:15:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 这下四周都清干净了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.64,0:15:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让任何一个人逃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:33.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家赶紧逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家赶紧逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.76,0:15:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要逃的家伙就自己逃走好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.39,0:15:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙由我来击溃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,招式完全被看破了 你还真敢说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.37,0:15:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是白痴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.73,0:15:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么就不懂得力量的悬殊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.97,0:15:53.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么看都不是同一个级别的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.77,0:15:54.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.61,0:15:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:16:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管他脾气怎么样 但小胜绝对不是没有脑子的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因材适用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.22,0:16:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近有很多职业英雄做不到这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小胜是在 尽他所能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.86,0:16:13.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很痛啊 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.86,0:16:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.57,0:16:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.51,0:16:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经强到可以随便的操心他人安危了吗？啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.04,0:16:33.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有空在这里发愣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.21,0:16:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不赶紧带那些家伙从这里逃出去啊 你这渣渣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.08,0:16:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不说一些讨人厌的话就不能好好地战斗吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.65,0:16:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 喂 爆豪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.82,0:16:46.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说那些家伙 是不是有些过了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一年A班20人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.06,0:16:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且我们全员都是志愿成为英雄的！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.10,0:16:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是团结啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.41,0:17:07.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.63,0:17:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A班
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.11,0:17:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到全员一起冲过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.81,0:17:42.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是意料之外的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.25,0:17:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但只有这点程度的话是不能把我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.19,0:17:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小胜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.20,0:18:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饭田君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.71,0:18:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,峰田君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.28,0:18:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛙吹 小梅雨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.68,0:18:07.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有一个想法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.16,0:18:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也应该累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多也该有个了结了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别逗我笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还早得很！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.47,0:18:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.94,0:18:27.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.81,0:18:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛙吹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.44,0:18:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我小梅雨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.74,0:18:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉螺牙天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解除
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.83,0:18:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁着爆炸的时机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.39,0:18:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.77,0:18:59.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能行的 Smash!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.78,0:19:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还 还是不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,垃圾还是闪一边去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.22,0:19:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是由我来击垮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.63,0:19:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活该
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.64,0:19:34.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「粘虫胶」计划真是完美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.51,0:19:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来他就完全动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.17,0:19:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 在攻击轨道上的攻击诱导也很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都跟计划的一样 绿谷君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:44.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小久 真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.35,0:19:47.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的做的 很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.52,0:19:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都是托大家的福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.06,0:19:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.79,0:19:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一瞬间就理解了我的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.39,0:19:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利用最大的力量把敌人给揍飞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.20,0:20:04.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然你是一个非常厉害的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:07.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动 动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该做个了结了 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.67,0:20:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等 等一下 我 是我 我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.35,0:20:17.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.21,0:20:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欧尔麦特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.12,0:20:20.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 哈哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我是想把这个不在敌联出现时的救助训练
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.69,0:20:25.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为一个惊喜的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.99,0:20:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 之前不是才发生了那种事么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.96,0:20:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.93,0:20:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是比我想象的要更加出类拔萃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.76,0:20:34.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是 英 诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.97,0:20:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总感觉…对不起大家了1
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.41,0:20:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得太过了吧 欧尔麦特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.04,0:20:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就跟前辈说的一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.55,0:20:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是不太适合啊 那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.62,0:20:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惊喜？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.35,0:20:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.59,0:20:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是反对的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.92,0:20:58.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.12,0:21:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A班4天前才受收到过敌联的袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.93,0:21:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们都以为那次袭击只是一次事故
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在几千甚至是几万分之一的概率里才会发生的偶然事件
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.57,0:21:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但事实并非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为英雄就会有数不尽的危机在前面等着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.94,0:21:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望他们能够对这件事有所自觉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.51,0:21:18.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不敢苟同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.58,0:21:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不好可是会造成心理阴影的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.18,0:21:25.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是要让他们具备跨越那些障碍的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.78,0:21:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不觉得那才是作为教师的我们应该做到的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.96,0:21:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就请你负好这个责任哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.23,0:21:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 我相信他们的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 全员都能够勇敢的站出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.30,0:21:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是吃了一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.10,0:21:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.47,0:21:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么样也要有个度啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.38,0:21:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？轰？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.21,0:21:58.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙 也是这个屎一般惊喜的共犯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.85,0:22:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.96,0:22:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我啊 轰少年
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.23,0:22:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能帮我一个忙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.67,0:22:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.90,0:22:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太过分了 欧尔麦特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.60,0:22:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说抱歉啦 我不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.84,0:22:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 绿谷少年的手指负伤也是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.41,0:22:27.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于此事 作为校方 是否非常的不妥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.71,0:22:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次不能再这样了啊！欧尔麦特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.41,0:22:31.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 小久
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.25,0:22:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 只是个惊喜 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.63,0:22:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绿谷少年
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.60,0:22:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么绿谷少年不少年的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.26,0:22:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.27,0:22:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小久
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.00,0:22:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去恢复女郞那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.40,0:22:52.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太 太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.24,0:26:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间是有限的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.88,0:26:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继承到力量的人 是我l
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.51,0:26:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雄英体育祭渐渐逼近
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.08,0:26:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是英雄们绝对不会错过的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.40,0:26:40.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你来过这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.83,0:26:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向全世界宣告出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.70,0:26:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解 欧尔麦特
